---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Get the Letters | Chaos With Clarity"
  description="An occasional letter with thoughts Abby doesn't share on Instagram or YouTube. Drafts, behind-the-scenes, and questions still being figured out."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section style="min-height:80svh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;text-align:center;padding:6rem 3rem 6rem;position:relative;background:var(--bg-alt);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">

    <p style="font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--olive-accent);margin-bottom:1rem;font-weight:600;">Stay in the Clarity</p>

    <h1 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:clamp(3rem,8vw,7rem);font-weight:800;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-bottom:0.75rem;line-height:0.92;">Get the Letters</h1>

    <p style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--olive-accent);font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;letter-spacing:0.01em;font-weight:500;">Honest notes from the middle of it all.</p>

    <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.95rem;max-width:30rem;line-height:2.1;margin-bottom:3rem;font-weight:300;">
      Thoughts I don't share on Instagram or YouTube.<br/>
      Drafts. Behind-the-scenes process. Questions I'm still figuring out.<br/>
      No spam. No "daily grind" tips. Just honest notes.
    </p>

    <!-- Our design, Kit backend -->
    <form
      id="cwc-form"
      style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.6rem;width:100%;max-width:22rem;"
    >
      <input
        type="email"
        id="cwc-email"
        placeholder="your@email.com"
        required
        style="background:var(--bg-alt);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);font-size:0.92rem;padding:1rem 1.1rem;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:400;outline:none;width:100%;transition:border-color 0.2s;"
        onfocus="this.style.borderColor='var(--gold)'"
        onblur="this.style.borderColor='var(--border)'"
      />
      <button
        type="submit"
        id="cwc-btn"
        style="font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;background:var(--gold);color:var(--bg);padding:1rem 1.5rem;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:600;transition:background 0.2s;"
        onmouseover="this.style.background='var(--olive-bright)'"
        onmouseout="this.style.background='var(--gold)'"
      >
        Get the Letters
      </button>
      <p id="cwc-msg" style="display:none;font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-top:0.25rem;"></p>
    </form>

    <script is:inline>
      document.getElementById('cwc-form').addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        const email = document.getElementById('cwc-email').value;
        const btn = document.getElementById('cwc-btn');
        const msg = document.getElementById('cwc-msg');
        btn.textContent = 'Sending…';
        btn.disabled = true;
        try {
          const res = await fetch('https://app.kit.com/forms/9235299/subscriptions', {
            method: 'POST',
            headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' },
            body: 'email_address=' + encodeURIComponent(email)
          });
          if (res.ok || res.status === 200 || res.status === 303) {
            msg.textContent = 'Check your inbox to confirm. ✓';
            msg.style.display = 'block';
            btn.style.display = 'none';
            document.getElementById('cwc-email').style.display = 'none';
          } else {
            throw new Error();
          }
        } catch {
          msg.textContent = 'Something went wrong — try again.';
          msg.style.color = '#c0392b';
          msg.style.display = 'block';
          btn.textContent = 'Get the Letters';
          btn.disabled = false;
        }
      });
    </script>

    <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.78rem;margin-top:1rem;letter-spacing:0.06em;opacity:0.7;">No spam. Ever. Unsubscribe any time.</p>

    <blockquote style="margin-top:4rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:2.5rem;max-width:30rem;">
      <p style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1.2rem;line-height:1.8;">"Save pieces that bother you a little.<br/>They usually have something to show you."</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--olive-accent);letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0.75rem;font-weight:600;">Abby</p>
    </blockquote>

    <div style="width:1px;height:4rem;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,var(--border),transparent);margin-top:2.5rem;"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT ARRIVES -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:0 3rem 7rem;">

    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.25rem;margin-bottom:3.5rem;margin-top:5rem;">
      <div style="flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border);"></div>
      <p style="font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-muted);padding:0 1rem;white-space:nowrap;font-weight:600;">What arrives</p>
      <div style="flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border);"></div>
    </div>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:5rem;" class="what-grid">

      <div style="padding:2.5rem;border-right:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
        <i class="ph ph-pencil-line" style="font-size:2rem;color:var(--olive-accent);"></i>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--text);font-weight:700;">Poems</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.9;">New poems as they come, raw, unpolished, honest. The kind I'd share with a close friend over chai.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="padding:2.5rem;border-right:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg-alt);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
        <i class="ph ph-notebook" style="font-size:2rem;color:var(--text-muted);"></i>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--text);font-weight:700;">Essays &amp; Drafts</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.9;">Thoughts I'm still working through. Behind-the-scenes process. Questions I don't share anywhere else.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="padding:2.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
        <i class="ph ph-fire" style="font-size:2rem;color:var(--olive-bright);"></i>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--text);font-weight:700;">Circles</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.9;">Occasional invites to Chaos Circles, small group conversations for people who want to go deeper than surface.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Poem preview -->
    <div style="max-width:44rem;margin:0 auto;border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:4px solid var(--olive-accent);padding:3rem 3.5rem;">
      <p style="font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--olive-accent);margin-bottom:0.75rem;font-weight:600;">A taste</p>
      <h3 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:0.4rem;font-weight:700;">Let Me Be Conscious</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--text-faint);font-size:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1.75rem;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-weight:600;">2025</p>
      <div style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:1.05rem;line-height:2.2;margin-bottom:1.75rem;">
        <p>Let me breathe today, let me be conscious,</p>
        <p>Let me be free today, let me be outrageous,</p>
        <p>Let me feel the pain I keep hiding,</p>
        <p>Let me kiss a plant today I keep avoiding.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/writings" style="font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--olive-accent);text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.4rem;font-weight:600;">
        Read all writings <i class="ph ph-arrow-right"></i>
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>


</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .what-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .what-grid > div { border-right: none !important; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .what-grid > div:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    section { padding-left: 1.5rem !important; padding-right: 1.5rem !important; }
  }
</style>
